text: Stefan Ledóchowski, Szaława coat of arms (died 1732), was Volhynian Podstoli in the years 1720–1727. In 1729 he was member of parliament in Volhynian Voivodeship in Polish–Lithuanian Commonwealth. == Bibliography == * Urzędnicy wołyńscy XIV-XVIII wieku. Spisy. Oprac.
